UMantashe ubethula ubufakazi egameni le-ANC phambi kweKhomishini kaZondo. Uthe owayeyisikhulu esiphezulu kwi-Oakbay, uMnuz Nazeem Howa, wababhalela incwadi ecela ukuthi ahlanganiswe nezikhulu ze-ANC. “UHowa wayegcizelela udaba lokulahleka kwemisebenzi uma kuvunyelwa ukuvalwa kwama-akhawunti ezinkampani zamalungu omndeni wakwaGupta,” kusho uMantashe. Ngaphambi kokuthi uMantashe athule ubufakazi, kuqale uMnuz Mzwanele Manyi oke waba yiNhloko yoPhiko lwezokuXhumana kuhulumeni iGCIS. - ANA